Germany Lobbies for Extensive Haircut on Greek Debt, FTD Says

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-10-10T07:20:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/germany-lobbies-for-extensive-haircut-on-greek-debt-ftd-says.html
German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s
government is lobbying for an extensive haircut on Greek debt,
the  Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing unidentified
government officials.  Germany ’s government considers a Greek insolvency
unavoidable in the long run, the newspaper said today. The topic
was supposed to be discussed at a meeting between Merkel and
French President Nicolas Sarkozy last night, the FTD said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
